msgs.Content: It was an early day, at school. Dib sat in his class, as he noticed Zim a little late but walk in.
Zim walked in with a blank face and just sat at his seat not careing
Dib looked at him, just 2 seats away from him, as he looked down at a journal, prepared to write notes for class
Ms sour glances around the class narrowing her eyes 'I hope you all are actually paying attention" starts writing on the borad
zim just picks at the the table with his claw
Glances to Zim
continues picking at desk

Continues looking at him, _Hm, must be up to something as usual...maybe he's planning on blowing up the world later? Or destroy me...sounds interesting. Its fun to stop him._ "fun..?" Accidentally questioned himself out loud
"is there something fun about failing a test dib"? Ms sour asked after just telling them that if they didn't take down the notes on the board they would fail

"Huh? Oh, um no! sorry Ms. Sour..." He then quickly wrote down what was on the board. He was confused at what he thought before. Of course it was fun for him, but it was very serious, he wasn't supposed to do it for fun, but to save the world. And he looked forward to  stopping him once again....he blushed slightly, confused but ignored it.
she rolls her eyes and continues writing and yelling at student
Soon throughout the class he grew bored, and doodled small drawing of Zim yelling
leaves large scratches in the desk thinking of what he will do next
He looked over at Zim's desk, hearing the scratches for so long
Zim just keeps on picking and scratching at the desk with his claw like hands
He continued staring at it "why are you ruining the desk?" He whispered to Zim, looking at his suspiciously
Zim gave him a deadly glare "none of your business stupid human flilth"
"I think it is, what are you doing? Why destroy your desk by scratching it?" He glared at him back
"it has nothing to do with you" Zim narrowed his eyes at him
"Does this have something to do with your next plan?!" He ripped out the page of doodles of Zim, crumbled it up and threw it at him
Zim catches the paper "no"
He blushed slightly when he remembered that page was filled of drawings of him "open that paper and your dead."
He just smirked and opened up the paper
"I SAID NOT TO!" he tried to get the paper away from him
he hold the paper out of reach "hey teacher dibs trying to take my notes" he smirked putting the paper and mixes it with his other notes and papers
He blushed "w-what?! No! Give that paper back!" He grew embarrassed knowing he had the paper
"dib leave zim alone already"! she shouted looking over at them
"He took my paper!" Goes to Zim to grab it back
"hey back off these are mine" holds up a piece of paper "see my handwriting"! glares pushing dib away
He tried to search around in his papers but couldn't find what he was looking for, he gave up and glared at him "dookie face...." he mutters and goes back to his seat
smirks watching dib go back to his desk
Sits back down at his seat, glaring at Zim the whole time, upset that he'll see all his drawings of him and make fun of him
pulls the paper out and looks at it
He looked away from him and looked out the window
hears the lunch bell go "alright go eat that slop the skool calls food" she waves her hand dismissively letting them go
He quickly left the room and went to lunch, and tried to avoid seeing Zim
he puts the paper inside a compartment in his pak and leaves the room
He left to go get lunch, then sit at a table with his sister Gaz
he sits by himself like usual but this time he didn't even bother to get a tray of food to pretend to eat
Dib looked at him from his lunch table "Look Gaz, he didn't even pretend to eat. And he took my paper of doodles! I wonder whats up with him, must be a new plan..." he eats as he looked away from Zim
grips the newest game slave 5 annoyed "dib why don't you just shut up already zim this zim that never ending zim zim zim"! she growled
"I suppose I do talk about him a lot...." he blushed slightly and sighed "do you think there's something wrong with me? I have felt strange...am I crazy?"
"are you just now asking if your crazy"? gives him a quick glance thinking
He sighed "never mind..." he looked at Zim again, wondering what he thought when he saw his doodles of him
continues thinking then smirks at the thought
He continued eating, looking at her "what are you thinking?"
smirks playing her game "oh nothing"
"This is why I'll never understand you..." he finishes his lunch and glances over to Zim
staring at the table gripping the chair angrily
Looks at him confused "maybe I could make some alien mind reader device..."
"heres a thought go talk to him"
"Confront him?! No way! He'll probably just attack me, and its weird to just ask him ___"___ whats up? ___"___ for no reason..." he continued looking at Zim
"whatever" she gets up and leaves
glaring down angrily at the table
goes over to zim "oi dib wants to know why your acting so strange and I want him to shut up"
"go away stupid purple hair human female"! he shouted still looking at the table
"I only came over cause dib wont shut up so tell me whats up so I can tell him and he can shut up" She glared at him
"I SAID GO AWAY"!! he stood up and ripped the chair up throwing it at her
she jumps out of the way "psycho"! she shouted glaring at him
he just glares and storms out of the cafeteria
goes back to her lunch
kicking a wall behind the school angrily "argh that stupid earth worm"! he growled clenching his fist angrily
He watched, surprised and scared at what happened "are you ok? He so angry...." he watched Zim leave
"I'm just fine" she goes back to playing her game and eating lunch at the same time
He stands up and decides to go to where Zim is and looks at him, going to him carefully "you broke a chair...."
glares at him "and I'll break you to"!
"So why the hell are you so angry?" He steps a little closer
"go away dib-worm"! He growled
"I'm asking a question you lizard! Answer it!" He glared at him and crossed his arms
he looked around and picked up a lead pipe that was nearby "and I said to go away"
He took a step back and continued glaring "just answer, Zim."
"no" Zim returned the glare gripping onto the pipe
He quickly gripped onto the pipe so then he wouldn't be able to hit him with it "TELL ME!"
glares at him "leave me alone dib or I WILL kill you"!! he pulls the pipe out of dibs grip
"Its not like you haven't already tried and ___failed___!" He tries to grip back onto it
suddenly grins looking insane "then just let me try again"!
He looks at him slightly frightened "just tell me what's wrong with you...."
"why the heck does it matter to you we're enemies remember stupid idiot"! he lifts the pipe and swings it at his head
He tried it dodge but it hit him on the head and he winced sharply in pain "I-I'm just curious!"
" I don't care how curious you are"!!! Zim glared and lifted up the pipe again
"Please! I don't understand!" He stepped back
"you don't need to understand your just a stupid pathetic earth creature"!! swings the pipe at him again
He dodges and grabs the pipe "I'm worried about why your so upset! Just....let me know, please?"
he just glares and lets go of the pipe "shut up dib" he turns and walks right out of skool
He dropped the pipe and followed him
looks back and glares at him "STOP FOLLOWING ME"!
"Just let me know...."

Zim turns and grabs his throat "why so you can just trick me"?! she glared digging his claws into his neck "tick me into thinking you actually care and into a false sense of secutrity"?!!! "well it wont work STUPID HUMAN"!!
*he glared
He coughs and tries to kick him "I-I'm....I'M NOT IF I _DO_ CARE!"
"LIAR ENEMIES DONT CARE ABOUT EACH OTHER"!! Zim throws him at a wall then continues back to his base
He gasps slightly and watches him leave and looks down, mutters "sorry....." he slowly stands up, and goes back into the school
Zim walks back to his house slamming the door open
Later that day, after school Dib made his way to Zim's house, but stood outside the fence way
He sighed and stared at the house, deciding whether or not to approach
singing loudly from the kitchen "ooooh tacos tacos I love you tacos tacos I'm gonna eaaat you"
Slowly goes to the front door
opens a window and hangs out of it "hi mary"!
"H-Hi....could you let me in?"
"hmmm...ok mary"!! he goes back inside and opens the door then sits on the couch that now has long slashes across it as well as the walls and most objects destroyed
He frowned slightly when looking around "Zim....where is he?"
"oooh masta was mad and then he destroyed stuff then he went to his beddy room"
He goes to where Zim is
hes laying on his bed eyes closed the walls are scratched up and wires ripped up and other objects broken and smashed
He sat down besides his bed, then gently put his hand on Zim's hand
"gir go away" he says thinking its gir trying to bug him
He gently gripped his hand "Zim...."
"go away dib"
"Please let me know whats wrong."
" I said go away"! he opened one eye to give him a stern look
"Zim..." Sits onto the bed, looking at him "Look, I'm seriously concerned."
"why"? tilts head to look at him "why are you so concerned"
" maybe because your destroying everything...."
"don't I usually destroy everything"?
"This is.....different."
"whats the difference"?
"Your upset. Tell me whats wrong. I came all the way here for you
sighs "why don't you just capture me and have me dissected"?
"I don't want to. Tell me whats wrong. I actually came to you to ask....I wouldn't if I didn't care."
he opens both eyes and looks at him then sits up
"So, please tell me." He looks at him worried

"last night I received a call from my leaders....it turned out they were calling cause now the funniest joke in irken history was starting to get annoying..the joke was me and my mission it was all a fake at first it was so I would die but then I didn't die and then they just laughed at all my plans and reports..." He clenched up his fist getting angry " I was nothing but a joke to them"!!! He reached up to a loose wire and ripped it down taking part of the wall with it and threw it across the room smashing it
"A joke...? But...your not a joke to me. I spent years trying to stop you, your strong. Why would they think that? That's stupid...." he stood up and went to him
"cause I'm the smallest and the smallest are the weakest and the stupidest" he crossed his arms still mad
"I devoted my life to stopping you....weak? I don't think so. Your strong. I treated you as if you were earths biggest threat! Your not weak!"
"that's your opion"
"I hate your Tallest" he hugged him quick "it doesn't matter what they say."
Zim just sat there letting dib hug him "I thought you hated all aliens"
"I don't hate you."
"why not" zim reached up and took out his contact lens

"Because.....your different than everyone. Remember how everyone ignores me or makes fun of me for being crazy? You didn't. You gave me attention....you thought of me as someone who could stop you. Having you around, felt fun. Like I had a meaning in life ...." he looked at him and blushed slightly and smiled "we short of go through the same thing."
"yea but now what...I don't need to take over this stupid planet so now you don't have a reason to stop me"

"So? Being with you was good. Plus, I hate everyone here, but I'm stuck living here too. Do you think....we could, be friends maybe..?" He looked slightly nervous "please don't kill me for saying that...."
"hrm...." thinking...."I suppose"
"Whoa, really?" He smiled "good. So...we can just like, hang out often then?"
nods
"so, your leaders don't care about you?"
"Yes..." He looked down angrily "They would never care what happens to me."
"Well now I'm your friend, so I'll always care about you" he looked at Zim and smiled
He did a very small smile back
A few days later, at Dibs home, Zim comes over
"So what should we do? Watch a movie?"
He shruged
He put on a movie, and sat onto the couch in the living room, watching it with Zim besides him
Watches the movie
After a long while, the movie is just about to end as two boys are very sleepy
Zim yawned slightly,  leaning back on the couch

After the movie finished, Dib looked over at Zim, noticing how he now fell asleep "...I'm sorry for this....." he whispers, picking Zim up, and heading down to his father's lab. He set zim on an examination table and strapped him down
He murmurs something in his sleep and whined slightly
"I'm sorry, I'm sorry, I'm sorry, I'm sorry, I'm sorry...." he slowly got materials, and got a dissection knife and marked where to cut.
Zim slowly woke up, and looked around slowly, until his eyes widened looking at Dib "DIB! W--"
He interrupted Zim by saying sorry repeatedly and dropped the materials

He used his pak legs to break him out and escape, angrily looking at Dib full of hatred "you....you tricked me. YOU don't care either" his eyes slowly showed tears starting up as he angrily glared. And he left the lab
"Z-Zim!" He went to go follow him and tried to stop him from leaving.
He tured around and faced him, as tears ran down his face, as he continued glaring
He looked at him surprised..._I've never....seen him like this. He was really upset about the Tallest, but didn't see him cry. I feel horrible...I went against him._
He slapped Dib hard and knocked him down with his pak legs, and left him

He was even more shocked when he did that and slowly slid down a wall and sat down on the floor. He looked down and teared up slightly "what the hell fid I do? I'm a monster...I wanted him to trust me....I miss him already...." he hugged around his legs "I.....wanted more than friendship.....I....I like Zim." He was surprised to hear himself say that as a tear escaped his eye, he shut his eyes tightly and cried softly to himself

Zim slowly cried angrily at his house and stormed into his room, slamming the door shut and grabbed a pipe and smashed it against the wall, making a large hole as he gripped his head tightly, while crying and trying to calm down.
The next day at school was horribly quiet. Zim looked upset and Dib was a mess
He threw notes at Zim, trying to get him to read them as he got ignored,he eventually stopped and looked down and raised his hand "may I.....go to the bathroom?"
"Yes, now hurry."
He left the room looking down. Later he noticed Zim leave the room and went to him "Zim....."
"Go away." He gave him a glare and looked away
He quickly hugged him tightly "I let my instincts get the best of me.....Zim, I care about you. I....." he kissed him quickly and pulled away "I like you, I love you....."
His expression softened a bit as he looked at Dib, and hugged him "Dib-thing....."
He embraced each other tightly and said how much they were sorry. This was it. The end of the crying and fear. The end of the fights. And the beginning of their new, stronger relationship.
